

=Bio=

Kevin Hansen (US). Independent filmmaker, environmental activist and geophysicist working on a feature documentary about the Commons. For this project, our crew has filmed in 29 locations showing many working old Commons and emerging new Commons. We will show ancient indigenous Commons, and focus on food, water, air, land, genetics, open-source movement, Commons law and the role of young people. Many Commons experts have already been filmed. Expected film release date is 2014.


